<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>٦٧٦١ - حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/3">آدَمُ، </a>حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/2779">شُعْبَةُ، </a>حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/6245">مُعَاوِيَةُ بْنُ قُرَّةَ</a> <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/5183">وَقَتَادَةُ، </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/822">أَنَسِ بْنِ مَالِكٍ </a><span class="special">﵁</span>،<span class="c5"> عَنِ النَّبِيِّ <span class="special">ﷺ</span> قَالَ:</span> <span class="c2">«مَوْلَى الْقَوْمِ مِنْ أَنْفُسِهِمْ»</span> أَوْ كَمَا قَالَ.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>